insertExistingRole

public static Role insertExistingRole(Role aObject)
                               throws DatabaseException
Used to insert a role object whose role id is already known, mostly used mostly during importing objects from an external source during creation of a new BA. So, be cautious if you want use this method, instead user insert which generates a new role id for a role being added.

Parameters:
aObject - object of type Role
Returns:
role object after insertion
Throws:
DatabaseException
